{"tid":542620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知你睇唔睇到 希望今次係我最後一次諗起你","createTime":"2018-01-27T16:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T19:07:30.000Z","uid":72536,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02e39edec49ceb031e2076c004471c110b749b31","tid":542620,"uid":72536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"兩年前嘅年尾 我地突然有機會熟<br />\n之後一齊有好多唔同嘅經歷 去挑戰<br />\n都係嗰句 有好多細微嘅事<br />\n令我鍾意咗你 成日想同你有多啲接觸<br />\n仲鼓起咗勇氣表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然你跳過咗<br />\n<br />\n跟住又因為一啲原因 我開始避你<br />\n避你係因為我見你同另一個friend玩得好埋<br />\n我就覺得 我唔應該對你再有咩感覺了<br />\n唔想好似同個friend爭男仔咁<br />\n之後開始多嘢做 工作令我慢慢好似忘記咗對你嘅感覺<br />\n冇再諗你 我都決定 <br />\n2018年應該從新開始 唔再帶呢種感覺去新一年<br />\n但啱啱又睇到個post :異性對你做咗啲令你感動嘅野<br />\n搞到我又諗起當時嘅你了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣吧 我唔知你會唔會睇到<br />\n睇到嘅 而你又對我有意思 不如試下同我講返嘢？<br />\n比啲singal我<br />\n其實我仲有啲掛住你 只係 怕 怕你已經有意中人<br />\n同時間地 都想自己忘記你<br />\n鍾意一個人原來都好辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係真係 如果個天冇比你見到個post<br />\n又或者你睇到都唔想理嘅<br />\n咁呢次 就係我最後一次想念著你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2da5453d17283429460cdbc3f7d8b40e175490e","tid":542620,"uid":78622,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"夜啦瞓喇 無人會記得你嫁"},{"pid":"16937b4e7c157126494c8f291ff813f538a69a76","tid":542620,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d49eb284912a281a2954fa83a3cd7b208fd0e36","tid":542620,"uid":26442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"明白既 要忘記一個人真係好難<br />\n自己都等過個女仔七年幾八年"},{"pid":"be9fe0fd5c5da01fc09d6449666e9bf3a50fddab","tid":542620,"uid":161537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"點解係佢搵你唔係你搵佢？"},{"pid":"a7d0382bc89a7494b4c0a53413e80859ecbe86f2","tid":542620,"uid":68258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"你開完個post咪又會期待人地會睇到揾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfb23ba48c88515e685fa966b4b50c9b1c341a6","tid":542620,"uid":107902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"都兩年了 都有戀人了吧"},{"pid":"489df52f2d1b43e431778789ee9281dde4c92fc1","tid":542620,"uid":137387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"何不將這雙手放進心裡"}]}